{
  "stem": "13141.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But with that visa, maybe you can get a transit visa through Spain or Portugal to get out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he gave us this visa in our passports.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we needed now a, a ship, you know, to-- I mean, officially to take us to Liberia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We knew we couldn't-- never go to Liberia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By the way, the capital of Liberia is Monrovia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's in Africa, West Africa, where that belly of Africa comes out, sticks out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's where Liberia is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't know it at the time, but I looked it up in the map.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we-- I remember we bought mosquito netting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We bought rubber boots because you couldn't get any leather boots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we, we got malaria tablets, and-- even though we knew we probably would never to get to Liberia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But still, for us, it was Liberia, you know, in our minds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Stuttgart, in the Auswandererstelle, we inquired.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told that we-- the only possibility to get out was on a freighter, on a freighter from, from Spain to Liberia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were coming there about once every three weeks or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we called up the Spanish Consulate in Munich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a Graf-- Backenheim was his name, Von Backenheim-- Count Von Backenheim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we told him that we had-- he was an honorary consul.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was an honorary consul for Spain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, we shouldn't forget that the Civil War in Spain was just over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans had helped, you know, the Franco to win that war against the Communists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we contacted that consulate, the Spanish Consulate in, in Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
